                        <div class="image-content"><p class="b1"></p></div>
                    </div>
                    <p class="card-title h6 highlight__slide-title">Shock Absorption</p>
                    <p class="b1">At heel strike, the carbon fiber absorbs impact, reducing the joint load on the lower
                        extremities</p>
                </div>


                <div class="card-highlight highlight__swiper-slide" style="margin-right: 10px;">
                    <div class="image-mask-wrapper">
                        <div class="image-mask">
                            <div class="image-mask__img-box hiw-highlight-mask">
                                <div class="image image-mask__image img-loaded hiw-highlight-bg"
                                     style="background-image: url({{ 'support-stabilty.jpg' | file_url }})">
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="image-content"><p class="b1"></p></div>
                    </div>
                    <p class="card-title h6 highlight__slide-title">Support & Stability</p>
                    <p class="b1">At “ footflat ”, VKs provide improved support and stability. Torquing or twisting of
                        the foot can lead to injury VKTRY Insoles help to reduce the chance of that happening</p>
                </div>


                <div class="card-highlight highlight__swiper-slide" style="margin-right: 10px;">
                    <div class="image-mask-wrapper">
                        <div class="image-mask">
                            <div class="image-mask__img-box hiw-highlight-mask">
                                <div class="image image-mask__image img-loaded hiw-highlight-bg"
                                     style="background-image:url({{ 'energy-storage.jpg' | file_url }})">
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="image-content"><p class="b1"></p></div>
                    </div>
                    <p class="card-title h6 highlight__slide-title">Energy Storage</p>
                    <p class="b1">When you prepare to push off the ground, you bend your foot and “load” the VKTRY
                        Insole. Passive energy will soon turn to kinetic</p>
                </div>


                <div class="card-highlight highlight__swiper-slide" style="margin-right: 10px;">
                    <div class="image-mask-wrapper">
                        <div class="image-mask">
                            <div class="image-mask__img-box hiw-highlight-mask">
                                <div class="image image-mask__image img-loaded hiw-highlight-bg"
                                     style="background-image: url({{ 'energy-return.jpg' | file_url }})">
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="image-content"><p class="b1"></p></div>
                    </div>
                    <p class="card-title h6 highlight__slide-title">Energy Return</p>
                    <p class="b1">Like a spring, the deflected VKTRY carbon fiber insole wants to return to it's natural
                        shape.
                        As you push off, the VK returns the energy that you had stored, propelling you forward or upward
                        with greater force. </p>

                </div>

            </div>

        </div>
    </div>

</section>

